{"tid":1947564,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[有請小鳳姐]警方指8名與確診女警有密切接觸警員 5人初步呈陰性","createTime":"2020-03-28T11:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T12:12:07.000Z","uid":326897,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2f730a6eecbc72c3a5fa5f8ebe04380333745acd","tid":1947564,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:15:50.000Z","msg":"警方指8名與確診女警有密切接觸警員 5人初步呈陰性<br />\n2020-03-28 HKT 19:04<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517462-20200328.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517462-20200328.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq9%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=76ddc545\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1517462-20200328.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=088f60bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1517462-20200328.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n日前一名駐守深水埗警署的22歲女警員確診感染新型肺炎，警方在社交網站上表示，有8名駐守深水埗分區的警務人員被界定為密切接觸者，當中5人初步檢測結果呈陰性，其餘3人正等候檢測。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，8名密切接觸者已到檢疫中心進行檢疫，當中兩人昨日入住火炭駿洋邨檢疫中心，其餘6人今日入住火炭駿洋邨及鯉魚門度假村檢疫中心。<br />\n<br />\n警方又指，一名曾經與確診女警接觸的槍械訓練科人員，雖未被界定為密切接觸者，但亦已接受測試，正等候檢測結果，警方已安排她暫停槍械訓練工作，減少與他人接觸。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">3萬 - 7啦</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"06cbe3a209b4dc5a19c412a32b568847639b81f5","tid":1947564,"uid":58413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:17:43.000Z","msg":"陰性都叫小鳳姐？"},{"pid":"fd1c578868aa57a680035b48b5dcf82692668bed","tid":1947564,"uid":169497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T11:19:29.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n咁都唔中<br />\n抽血就中兩個無辜嘅"},{"pid":"809de6602e1b5dbefdced174a5c1e85668d448b8","tid":1947564,"uid":326897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06cbe3a209b4dc5a19c412a32b568847639b81f5","tid":1947564,"uid":58413,"like":4,"dislike":0,"